Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.60,0:02:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}好久不見了，基爾議長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.48,0:02:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}真是粗暴的歡迎方式啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.28,0:02:41.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}我沒必要為失禮而道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.46,0:02:45.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}為了跟你好好談談這是必須的做法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.26,0:02:47.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}真是一點都沒變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.01,0:02:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}就不管我這邊方不方便嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.60,0:02:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}因為這個議題很緊急
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.28,0:02:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}這是不得已的辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.96,0:02:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}希望你能理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.87,0:02:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}沒想到不是委員會，而是{\rED} SEELE {\r}親自出面
